{"tid":2015109,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[執政意志] 學日文仔話一定要鼓勵外國人學香港話","createTime":"2020-05-13T12:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:17:08.000Z","uid":227811,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe56b8a8ee9875bf09585e9310d38d51789073b","tid":2015109,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EjNklm86k6M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEjNklm86k6M&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHKS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=abc859d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EjNklm86k6M</a><br />\n<br />\n早排有好多post 都提大家要堅持用香港話<br />\n唔好再用蝗語 除此之外 我哋仲要鼓勵多啲人學講<br />\n同韓流一樣 軟實力可以推廣到文化達致旅遊業蓬勃<br />\n我哋當年黃金年代  香港電影 廣東話歌 可以打通全世界<br />\n我哋要加油 慢慢鋪路 做返個朵出嚟 <br />\n如果要執政意志 如果想講到獨立嘅話 <br />\n其中一樣野 就係要創造引以為傲嘅文化<br />\n同埋要創造與別不同嘅野 去define自己 <br />\n就係  <span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人 HongKonger </span><br />\n<br />\n而家大家都知道 時代革命唔係一兩年可以搞掂<br />\n所以由而家開始 我哋要重新承傳同埋創造香港文化 <br />\n<br />\n學哩個日文仔話一定要鼓勵外國人學香港話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0T6WQgn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0T6WQgn.png&h=4be24d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y43KeH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY43KeH3.png&h=a9a64f48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd1d4b008b2807fb303777c113834ad90a4209aa","tid":2015109,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:12:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d11a5c795ac96a3214ebe612e4586e1f9357b28a","tid":2015109,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c4e0d732719bb15af66b015d2680998a28c1b19","tid":2015109,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c03bb6f6b05ae21913be63a69a66f70995730e55","tid":2015109,"uid":227811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20